SPACE_MGMT.journeyShortDescription: Create a new space and navigate to its asset listing page.
SPACE_MGMT.primaryUserGoal: To successfully create a new space and access the asset listing page to manage folders and assets.
SPACE_MGMT.potentialStartingPoints:
1. User is logged into the application
2. User is on the dashboard or home page
3. User has access to the "Create New" functionality
SPACE_MGMT.highLevelSteps:
1. Log in to the application with valid credentials.
2. Click on the Create New button.
3. Enter a valid space name and description.
4. Click on the Save button.
5. Open the newly created space.
6. Verify navigation to the Asset Listing page.
SPACE_MGMT.successOutcome:
1.Space is created successfully.
2. User is navigated to the Asset Listing page.
SPACE_MGMT.tearDownSteps:
1. Delete the created space (if required for test cleanup).
2. Remove any folders or assets created during the test execution.
